"{\"uid\": \"prnewswire.com-news-releases-equality-champions-team-up-to-advocate-for-gender-parity-in-the-olympic-games-with-elite-athlete-fundraising-dinner-at-edwins-too-in-cleveland-302048804.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Searching for your content...  In-Language News  Contact Us  888-776-0942from 8 AM - 10 PM ET  Jan 31, 2024, 08:41 ET  Share this article  CLEVELAND, Ohio,Jan.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 150, \"end\": 154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ohio\", \"score\": 0.9649368696656501, \"rank\": 0.03633484987956237, \"text\": \"Ohio\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ohio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ohio\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"31, 2024/PRNewswire/ --Heaven to the YeahandEdwins Leadership & Restaurant Institutehave joined forces to further gender parity in the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 309, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In celebration of the upcomingParis2024 Olympics, the two organizations will be hosting a fundraising dinner atEdwins TooinClevelandonSaturday, March 2nd, 2024.\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The event will featuretwo-time Olympic gold medalistChristian Taylor,2023 Pan American Games bronze medalistJordan Gray,Jamaican CAC silver medalistErica Belvit,French DecathleteAdeline Audigier, and additional Olympic hopefuls.\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 545, \"end\": 563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\", \"score\": 0.9987630572885893, \"rank\": 0.0008341464872045817, \"text\": \"Pan American Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.7549806760778245, \"rank\": 0.3004235835428503, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \