begin\": 2192, \"end\": 2199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omar_Little_and_associates\", \"score\": 0.5486643621832741, \"rank\": 0.7479959088843997, \"text\": \"Brandon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omar_Little_and_associates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omar_Little_and_associates\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Guests will also be among the first to sip on Heaven to the Yeah's\\\"Women's Decathlon Limited Edition\\\"Bordeauxwine.\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2338, \"end\": 2347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Decathlon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.48578056477047e-29, \"text\": \"Decathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Decathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Decathlon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join us for this opportunity to be a part of Olympic history and support the athletes in their pursuit of transformative inclusion with excellence!\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2526, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TICKETS:Available online throughEventbrite.\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A limited number of VIP tickets are available for those looking to experience an exclusive meet-and-greet along with passed drinks and hors d'oeuvres prior to dinner.\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A portion of the ticket cost is tax-deductible and event proceeds help to support funding for decathlon events.\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"DONATIONS:Unable to attend the event?\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Help us make history with a 100% tax-deductible donation here:https://www.heaventotheyeah.org/donate  Road toParis2024 & Beyondis made possible with the generous support of the following sponsors: Edwins Leadership & Restaurant Institute, Heaven to the Yeah, Eaton Corporation, and Edwins Too.\", \"from\": 2